    "Name": "Telesilla TEL-510",
    "Details": "The TEL-510 is the original Telesilla configuration, introduced in 3025 by Majesty Metals and Manufacturing as an experimental Magistracy Armed Forces medium BattleMech. A right-arm Binary Laser Cannon serves as the primary weapon, delivering heavy damage at the cost of severe heat generation that fifteen standard heat sinks struggle to manage under sustained fire. A left-torso LRM 5 and left-arm SRM 4 provide supplementary fire when heat forces the pilot to hold the main weapon. Ammunition for both missile systems is carried unprotected.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Combat Computer</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>",
